title: INFINITY - AGAINST THE TIDE 001 (2013) (Digital) (Zone-Empire)
description:
Infinity: Against The Tide Infinite Comic #1

INFINITY enters the digital realm! A million light-years from Earth, the awesomely powerful Builder armada grinds its way through inhabited systems in a trajectory towards the Earth, little caring who or what is ground up in its wake! But there's someone else who does care, and he's got the power to do something about it: the Silver Surfer!

Written by Jason Latour
Art by Agustin Alessio
Cover by Agustin Alessio

Genre: Superhero
84 Pages
Digital Release Date: Aug 14th 2013
Age Rating: 12+ Only
